---
title: Contact
layout: default
---

%section.text
  .intro
    :markdown
      I try to respond to email within 48 hours. You can use the contact form
      below, or get in touch directly: <{{ site.email }}>.

%section.contact
  .contact

    %form{ role: "form", id: "contact", action: "https://formspree.io/p@rdln.net", method: "post" }
      .form-group#name-field
        %label.control-label{ for: "name" } Your Name
        %input.form-control{ id: "name", type: "text", name: "name" }
      .form-group#email-field
        %label.control-label{ for: "name" } Your Email
        %input.form-control{ id: "name", type: "email", name: "email" }

      .form-group#message-field
        %label.control-label{ for: "message" } Your Message
        %textarea.form-control{ id: "message", name: "message", rows: 5 }

      .form-group#submit
        %button.btn.btn-primary{ type: "submit" } Say Hello
